differences imposed on people

00:16:40.090 --> 00:16:44.620
to differentiate them that
these people are untouchable.

00:16:44.620 --> 00:16:48.620
So, caste in India,
the society is divided

00:16:48.620 --> 00:16:50.210
into different castes.

00:16:50.210 --> 00:16:53.550
The top is Brahmins, they
are the purest caste.

00:16:53.550 --> 00:16:59.450
So, caste is -- has both -- two
things, occupation associated

00:16:59.450 --> 00:17:03.850
with it, and purity, pollution,
scale associated with it.

00:17:03.850 --> 00:17:08.070
The Brahmins at the top,
they're a priestly caste.

00:17:08.070 --> 00:17:11.660
They perform the priestly
functions, they're the purest.

00:17:11.660 --> 00:17:13.630
And the second is
Vais -- Vais --

00:17:13.630 --> 00:17:17.900
no, Kshatriyas, that
is the warrior caste.

00:17:17.900 --> 00:17:21.490
And the third is the Vaishyas,
the merchant, trader caste.

00:17:21.490 --> 00:17:25.630
And the fourth is a
conglomeration of subcastes,

00:17:25.630 --> 00:17:29.130
each defined by its occupation.

00:17:29.130 --> 00:17:33.390
Potters is one caste and
carpenters are one caste,

00:17:33.390 --> 00:17:37.690
diggers ar one cast, and
even prostitution is a caste.

00:17:37.690 --> 00:17:40.440
It's by birth that
you're a prostitute,

00:17:40.440 --> 00:17:44.380
not by your choosing,
not by your --

00:17:44.380 --> 00:17:47.600
circumstance, but
because you're born

00:17:47.600 --> 00:17:50.430
in a prostitute family,
