these people's occupation.

00:18:10.180 --> 00:18:13.840
And there is nothing one can
do to choose their caste,

00:18:13.840 --> 00:18:17.480
and there's nothing one can
-- that can do to escape.

00:18:17.480 --> 00:18:20.720
You're born into your
caste and you die in it.

