whether there is a
political solution,

00:43:09.260 --> 00:43:10.560
we only have two minutes, so --

00:43:10.560 --> 00:43:11.860
&gt;&gt; Sujatha Gidla: Yeah.

00:43:11.860 --> 00:43:13.160
&gt;&gt; Rumaan Alam: This is a big
-- this is a tall order for you.

00:43:13.160 --> 00:43:14.460
&gt;&gt; Sujatha Gidla: Yeah.

00:43:14.460 --> 00:43:15.760
&gt;&gt; Rumaan Alam: To answer
whether there is a political

