00:43:29.600 --> 00:43:30.900
&gt;&gt; Sujatha Gidla: Right.

00:43:30.900 --> 00:43:32.200
&gt;&gt; Rumaan Alam: That
it's really --

00:43:32.200 --> 00:43:33.500
and what you're talking about is
not just the breaking of castes,

00:43:33.500 --> 00:43:35.430
