larger capitalist --

00:43:35.430 --> 00:43:36.730
&gt;&gt; Sujatha Gidla: Yeah.

00:43:36.730 --> 00:43:38.030
&gt;&gt; Rumaan Alma: System.

00:43:38.030 --> 00:43:39.340
But, do you have any --
do you have any optimism

00:43:39.340 --> 00:43:40.640
or do you have any sense

00:43:40.640 --> 00:43:42.480
